{"tid":1587945,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"信念，是一種相信，相信它一定會發生的勇氣。","createTime":"2019-09-22T15:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T23:54:46.000Z","uid":41705,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f06691eee621a074029629385d3ad2fafcd56c38","tid":1587945,"uid":41705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"【BC Sunday ● 十月 &ndash; 信念 Uphold the Faith】<br />\n<br />\n信念，是一種相信，相信它一定會發生的勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n面對現實的重重難關，我們或許有過心灰意冷、因為迷惘而不知所措的時候。今個月BC Sunday帶來的四套電影，呈現四個備受國際喜愛的導演眼中為信念而戰的故事 &mdash; 有人堅持追尋真相、爭取法律上的公義；有人爭取生存的權利，亦有人實踐出對信仰的信心&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">電影提醒我們，在面對難關時，絕不能讓心中的那團火熄滅，因為能夠令心中熱誠點燃的，從來只有自己的信念。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70357155_2350550821659187_8206280170064052224_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQkuYhs4Yp2P4cHL7VTjRsdDcA__KurOm3nVJscohJsl3HRmB1BDCwfxjrXy4VjHiTA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=1c9b39874d7ccac9585dd3a5ca675c7e&amp;oe=5E3A12F9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70357155_2350550821659187_8206280170064052224_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQkuYhs4Yp2P4cHL7VTjRsdDcA__KurOm3nVJscohJsl3HRmB1BDCwfxjrXy4VjHiTA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D1c9b39874d7ccac9585dd3a5ca675c7e%26oe%3D5E3A12F9&h=06741369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bc.BroadwayCinematheque/photos/a.935689393145344/2350550818325854/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbc.BroadwayCinematheque%2Fphotos%2Fa.935689393145344%2F2350550818325854%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBtXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=4fa39adb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bc.BroadwayCinematheque/photos/a.935689393145344/2350550818325854/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"1111f7ec8a6106bf1ccad6721c009f1b5e1078d2","tid":1587945,"uid":47